|awards                = [[Royal Institute of British Architects|RIBA]] London Architecture Medal for 1929 (awarded 1931)&lt;br/&gt;[[Royal Gold Medal|RIBA Royal Gold Medal]] (1936)&lt;br/&gt;[[Royal Designers for Industry|Royal Designer for Industry]] (1943)
